{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_01","textHome":"呼……哈……冷静下来……得好好做自我介绍@才行……好！我是安积育梦。虽然不太擅长@同时做很多件事情，但我很喜欢做裁缝和编@制这种细致的工作。还有，我在戏剧社负责@服装和小道具的制作。……那个，从今以后@请多多关照……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":103000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":103000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103000}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_17","textHome":"那个，你平时会用遮盖胶带吗？因为我会不自@觉地买下来，所以总是会突然发现没地方放@了……如果可以的话，希望你能收下一些。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_18","textHome":"诶嘿嘿，不自觉地买下来了。小猫和小老鼠的@便签纸。弹弹的样子好可爱……哎？这只小@猫稍微有点像时雨呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_19","textHome":"嗯！交给我吧。我会用这份力量打倒魔女的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":103000,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_20","textHome":"……我知道，不能止步不前的……稍微努力一@下吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":103000,"motion":1}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_21","textHome":"就算成为了魔法少女，我也还是很半吊子。明@明能打赢魔女，却无法守护自己的领地……@但是，我想稍微拿出点勇气努力一下。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":103000,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_22","textHome":"如果没有魔法少女之间的争斗，我是不是也会@作为“绝对能打倒魔女的人”受到尊敬呢…@…我有时也会靠这种空想逃避。但是，现在@的我应该说得出口……“就算对方是魔法少@女，也能稍微战斗一下”……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":103000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":103000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":103000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":103000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1030_00_23","textHome":"灯花大人和音梦大人……还有姬，她们都是与@我生活在不同世界的人……不管如何期望，@我也无法与她们并肩站立。但是，我能为了@回应她们的期待而努力。那就是我能做到的@事情吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.6,"chara":[{"id":103000,"